               "text": "<p class=\"desc\"><img id=\"imgGeo27\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgGeo27', '0%')\" src=\"\" class=\"imgcenter\"/><b>Figure 1</b>: In this map, the continent is highlighted (<htcite0>).</p>",
