            {
               "text": "Rabbi Dr. Yitzchok Breitowitz, on the <i>Jewish Learning Institute</i>, reflects on the use of metaphor and allegory in sacred texts, noting how these elements may reflect historical events. Similarly, Dr. Abdul Karim Khan reminds us that concepts of creation and the world have emerged across different cultures, each with its own interpretations and symbolism",
